FNType

String with the name of the mathematical function.

Synopsis

typedef const char* FNType;
#define FNCOMBINE  "combine"
#define FNRATIONAL "rational"
#define FNEXP      "exp"
#define FNLOG      "log"
#define FNPHI      "phi"
#define FNSQRT     "sqrt"
#define FNINVSQRT  "invsqrt"

FNSetType(), FN
